3. Collections Tasks
A. Lists: Create a list of your favorite fruits. Write a program to add a new fruit to the list, remove a fruit from the list, and print the list.
#Collections Tasks

fruits = ['grape','apple','mango']
fruits.append('orange') # add item

remove = fruits.pop(2) # remove item with  index 2
print(fruits)
print(remove)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
B.Tuples: Create a tuple with numbers from 1 to 5. Write a program to print each element in the tuple.

Tup = (1,2,3,4,5)
print(type(Tup))
print(Tup)

for i in Tup:
    print(i)
