C.Dictionaries: Create a dictionary with keys as names and values as ages. Write a program to add a new name and age, update an existing age, and print the dictionary.

dict = {'Anu':23,'Revathy':30,'John':28}
print(dict)
# add new item

dict.update({'Biny':29,'Manu':31})
print(dict)
